Sangta te bhaxen amchea [[Gõy]] rajant donn pornea vo adlea goyinchi kobor amkam mel’lta. Dogaim-kui ho mann favo kiteak ek kallar tim donnuim rajganv aslole. Adlea goyam vo old Goa zaitea igorzanim nettiolam ani sonvsarak famad tourist zago to zala. Voddlea goyant ek kallar devllam aslolim punn atam tim nant. Dr. A S Altekar sangta tem pormonnem amkam Vhoddlem goy hem Govapuri vo Gove mhunn Ramanayanant melltam toxench Gopakapattana mhunn amlam Mahabaratant mellta. Ani tancho orth mhollear hea Rajacher konne nodor marlear tankam bhogsonnem meltit mhunn bhoriololem mhunn melta.
