== Vavr vo dhonddo ==

Voddlem Goyant lokan kall bodoleant nusteacho dhonddo ani xetkamot suru keli ani aplem pott bhorunk tem lagle. Konngam ani her bhaji rovpak ekdom famad ho ganv zalo. Tambdi bhaji, dhovi bhaji, mullo, vaigim, mirsango, moke, bhendde ani olsande atanchea kallar tim rovpak namnechi zaleant.dusro vavr dhonddo mhullear maddachi sur kaddop, ogranlem mitt kadop dhukrachea masachi chourisa korop ani kombeo pallop hem pasun atam asa punn atam lok ganv des soddun bhailea gavant ravpak lagun hi kama atam komi zait asat. Ani xetam rovpachi unni zaleant zominui padd zalea.
