== Jevonn ==

Sogllea goykara bhaxen vegllem nhoi sodancench Xitt koddi ani nustem. Konnganchem pikk kubh ani ek kavodd mhollear “Gauns” hi poddot. Konngam ukdon tacho chakri korun tellant kur-kurit ti bhaztat.

== Village life ==

Goa velha fokkot ani kantram ani football nhoi. Zaitea kannvolli and dhaktea kavpachea zaggeani atam bhorot asa. Goykar susegad mhunn hea gavant pasun amkam dissun yeta. Goa velhachea bazarant tum nodor marxi tukla sarkem distolem eka kallar ho ek famad zago.

Bus sthanak lagim sarko ho bazzar asa. Fantea parar ho bazzar susegadd jivit gheta.nustekaram sodanchea lokak ulo korit aplem nustem vinktat donnparchea vellar mhotso tar gheun portun sajechi yetat.
Gavant bhirot tum vexi vell sarpak dhonnparchi tuka bhurgim toxi zanttim kaddacho kell vo ghoddeancho kell kelltole mellta. Adlea kallar oxem zatalem atam TV yeuvn bhodlop zalamxem dista pun azzunnui amkam oslem dhekave melltat.
Xinkop zanar lok 80%, ani hem karan mhullear zaiti iskolam hea gavant asat. Tim mhollear St. Andrews High School, Immaculate Heart of Mary’s High School, Fr. Agnel’s Boys High School, Popular High School (Goa Board). The primary schools are Fairy Land School and Montessori. Pilar padrinim ani ek Fr. Agnel Central School hem CBSC board School uggodlam te bhair . Fr. Agnel Higher Secondary, Fr. Agnel College of Arts and Commerce, Pilar Music School, and Pilar Industrial training Institute Pilarche padre hea gavant saovlotti ditat.

Goa velha ek dhaktullem xar mhunnok zata hospital, pharmacies, gas station, post office ani banking sovlotti hea gavant asatat, gavant bhagaracho xett aplem shop ghalun asa, tea bhsir beauty parlours, ropache boutique ,gereji dhakti soda ani soft drinkanchi factory (Smith Drinks) ani borfachi Factory - Ice Kings – hea dhaktullea xarant asa. Zaddachi nursery indoor zaddachi ani and ornamental zaddachi dog bhav -Djanjo and Danny Pires hea gavant asa. Namneche Pereira brothers, Paulo Travels, ek famad vhanachem nanv, cohea ganvche. Goa Velha Ayurveda voktam meltalim. Ganvchea eka vaddeant – Zuari –ayurvedic voktam dhivpi ani haddache dhkik pot’teo vo pap martoleank Zuarioilo dotor oxem mhunntale. Atam hem kommi zala .Antonio D'Silva, goyant chourisam korpak famad ani zaito lok taka soddun yeta.

Igorjeachea fuddem ek kazarachem hall ‘casa de povo’ ani Goa Velha Sports club atam goychea football ligent kelta tea bhair tin ration shop asat.

